original_title: Dvořák: From The New World – Gewandhausorchester Leipzig, Andris Nelsons, Kristine Opolais
overview: Recorded live at the Gewandhaus zu Leipzig in May 2017, this release features a delightful concert by the Gewandhausorchester Leipzig and conductor Andris Nelsons. For the program, the conductor has chosen works by Antonin Dvorak, including the Othello Concert Overture, and his famous Symphony No. 9 in E minor- “From the New World.
title: Dvořák: From the New World
